<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="modern-page">
    <section class="inner-hero reveal-on-scroll">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Comprehensive travel solutions tailored to make your journeys seamless, memorable, and truly extraordinary.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="modern-content">
        <div class="services-section">
            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="tours">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/tours.jpg');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Guided Tours</h2>
                    <p>Embark on curated adventures led by passionate local experts. From thrilling safaris in Maasai Mara to the serene beauty of the Kenyan coast, our tours cover the most breathtaking destinations. Whether you seek adrenaline-pumping wildlife encounters or peaceful escapes, we design experiences that exceed expectations.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Big Five Safari Adventures</strong> — Witness lions, elephants, rhinos, leopards, and buffaloes in their natural habitat</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Cultural & Heritage Tours</strong> — Visit traditional villages, markets, and historical sites with local guides</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Mountain Expeditions</strong> — Conquer Mount Kenya and volcanic peaks with expert climbing guides</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Coastal & Beach Tours</strong> — Explore pristine beaches, marine parks, and water activities</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>City Walking Tours</strong> — Discover Nairobi's hidden gems, art scene, and culinary hotspots</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Romantic Getaways</strong> — Intimate dinners, sunset safaris, and secluded beach picnics for couples</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Book a Tour</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="car-hire">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/car-hire.jpg');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Car Hire</h2>
                    <p>Explore at your own pace with our diverse fleet of well-maintained vehicles. Whether you need a rugged 4x4 for off-road adventures or a comfortable sedan for city drives, we have the perfect vehicle for you. Plus, enjoy the flexibility of self-drive or our professional chauffeur service.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>4x4 Safari Vehicles</strong> — Land Cruisers and Defenders built for rough terrains and game viewing</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Economy Cars</strong> — Fuel-efficient compacts for budget-conscious travelers</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Luxury Vehicles</strong> — Premium sedans and SUVs for business and VIP travel</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Self-Drive rentals</strong> — Freedom to explore at your own pace with flexible pick-up/drop-off</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Chauffeur Services</strong> — Professional, licensed drivers for stress-free travel</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Airport Transfers</strong> — Reliable pickups and drop-offs for seamless travel</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Hire a Car</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="hotels">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/hotel-booking.webp');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Accommodation & Hotel Bookings</h2>
                    <p>Find the perfect stay for every need and preference. From luxury five-star resorts with stunning ocean views to intimate boutique hotels in the heart of the city. We understand that some guests require additional privacy and security—we've got you covered.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Luxury Resorts & Five-Star Hotels</strong> — Premium amenities, world-class service</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Boutique Hotels</strong> — Intimate, personalized stays</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Budget & Economy Accommodations</strong> — Comfort without compromise</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Eco-Lodges & Sustainable Stays</strong> — Nature-forward accommodations</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Discreet & Secure Accommodations</strong> — Private estates, gated properties, and exclusive villas for guests requiring maximum privacy and enhanced security</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Customised Accommodation</strong> — Tailored to your specific requirements, whether you need specific locations, special arrangements, or unique amenities</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Book a Stay</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="conferencing">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/conferrence.jpg');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Conferencing & Events</h2>
                    <p>Host your meetings, retreats, and events in settings that inspire productivity and connection. From state-of-the-art conference rooms to unique outdoor venues, we deliver seamless experiences tailored to your objectives. No matter the size or style of your event, we ensure every detail is handled.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Corporate Conferences</strong> — Professional venues with full AV support</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Executive Retreats</strong> — Focused away-from-it-all settings for strategy sessions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Team Building & Outdoor Venues</strong> — Adventure camps, bush lodges, and nature-based locations</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Board Meetings</strong> — Intimate, high-security settings for sensitive discussions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Workshops & Training Sessions</strong> — Flexible spaces with custom configurations</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Hybrid Events</strong> — Virtual and in-person attendance options</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Plan Your Event</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="flights">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/flights.webp');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Air Ticketing</h2>
                    <p>Navigate the skies with ease. Our air ticketing service offers competitive fares on domestic and international routes, with expert guidance to help you find the best connections and deals. We search across all major airlines to secure the best prices for you.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Domestic Flights</strong> — Quick connections within Kenya to Nairobi, Mombasa, Kisumu, and more</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>International Flights</strong> — Routes to Europe, Middle East, Africa, and worldwide destinations</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Multi-City Itineraries</strong> — Combine multiple destinations in one seamless booking</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Group Bookings</strong> — Special rates and coordinated seating for teams and families</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Last-Minute bookings</strong> — Urgent travel arrangements when you need them most</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Business Class</strong> — Premium cabin options for comfort-focused travelers</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Find Flights</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row reveal-on-scroll" id="packages">
                <div class="service-image reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-1" style="background-image: url('/images/packages.png');"></div>
                <div class="service-text reveal-on-scroll reveal-stagger-2">
                    <h2>Travel Packages</h2>
                    <p>Experience worry-free travel with our all-inclusive packages. We handle everything from flights and accommodations to activities and transfers, so you can focus on making memories. Every trip is tailored to your preferences—no two experiences are alike.</p>
                    <ul class="service-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Safari Packages</strong> — All-inclusive Big Five game drives with luxury lodge stays</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Beach Holidays</strong> — Coastal escapes to Mombasa, Diani, Malindi, and exotic island resorts</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Honeymoon & Romantic Getaways</strong> — Secluded villas, candlelit dinners, massage couples treatments, and sunset safaris</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Adventure Packages</strong> — Mount climbing, hiking, white-water rafting, and extreme sports</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Family Packages</strong> — Child-friendly activities, kids clubs, and family-sized accommodations</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Corporate Travel</strong> — Seamless business trips with meetings, transport, and team-building activities arranged</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/get-quotation" class="btn" style="margin-top: 2rem;">View Packages</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<script src="/js/scrollytelling.js"></script>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
